  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd - \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Samantha Power also discussed the India-Sri Lanka situation",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "USAID Chief Executive Samantha Power, who is on a visit to India, has also held discussions on the situation in Sri Lanka.",
        "Samantha Power visited India from 25th to 27th.",
        "International issues such as Sri Lanka's crisis and food crisis, climate change, are reported to have featured prominently in Samantha Power's talks in India.",
        "On the 26th, Samantha Power held talks with representatives of civil society organizations on several issues including freedom of expression and protection of the rights of minority groups.",
        "He expressed America's commitment to continue working with civil society to advance human rights and fundamental rights.",
        "Samantha Pawar also met the Indian External Affairs Minister and External Affairs Secretary and held talks.",
        "Saying that the purpose of this meeting is to reaffirm that India and the United States are strategic partners and collaborators in many development issues, USAIT's response speaker Sejal Pulivartiri said that they discussed the region, India's leadership, and America's assistance at a time when Sri Lanka is facing an economic crisis."
      ],
